<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- المُسْكِرُ المَائِعُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَا لَا يُؤْكَلُ مِنَ الطَّيْرِ وَالبَهَائِمِ مِمَّا فَوْقَ الهِرِّ خِلْقَةً:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>نَجِسٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَكُلُّ مَيْتَةٍ نَجِسَةٌ غَيْرَ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> مَيْتَةِ الآدَمِيِّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَالسَّمَكِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَالجَرَادِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَيُعْفَى عَنْ يَسِيرِ طِينِ شَارِعٍ عُرْفًا إِنْ عُلِمَتْ نَجَاسَتُهُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَإِلَّا فَهُوَ طَاهِرٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَلَا يُكْرَهُ سُؤْرُ حَيَوَانٍ طَاهِرٍ،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ فَضْلَةُ طَعَامِهِ وَشَرَابِهِ غَيْرَ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> دَجَاجَةٍ مُخَلَّاةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَفَأْرٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَلَوْ أَكَلَ هِرٌّ وَنَحْوُهُ أَوْ طِفْلٌ نَجَاسَةً ثُمَّ شَرِبَ -وَلَوْ قَبْلَ أَنْ يَغِيبَ-<span class="c5"> مِنْ مَاءٍ يَسِيرٍ:</span> فَطَهُورٌ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>